PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779987954
OL,3,CTributes paid to man as more arrests
OL,4,Cmade in murder investigation
OL,6,FHis family said: "Peter had a big
OL,7,Ffamily who all loved him, he was the
OL,8,Fheart and soul of our family. We are
OL,9,Fdevastated at his loss and feel we
OL,10,Fhave been robbed of him. We would
OL,11,Fappreciate privacy to grieve and come
OL,12,Fto terms with what has happened."
OL,14,FTwo more people have since been
OL,15,Farrested; a 39-year-old man on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of murder and a 29-year-old
OL,17,Fman on suspicion of assisting an
OL,18,Foffender.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
