PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779987954
OL,3,CTributes paid to man as more arrests
OL,4,Cmade in murder investigation
OL,6,FA second 39-year-old man, was was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of murder,
OL,8,Fremains in police custody along with a
OL,9,F38-year-old woman, arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender. A
OL,11,F28-year-old woman arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender,
OL,13,Fhas been bailed pending further
OL,14,Fenquiries.
OL,16,FA 67-year-old woman and a 65-year-old
OL,17,Fman who were arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fassisting an offender have since been
OL,19,Freleased with no further action.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
